---
title: Moroccan Honey Chicken & Crumbly Cheese with Roast Veggie Couscous & Lemon Yoghurt
description: We love the way honey caramelises in a pan, lending a crispy, sticky finish to chicken. We’ve used chicken thigh here
ecause it packs a fantastic flavour, remains moist as it cooks and complements the bed of delicious roast veggie
couscous that comes with it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-honey-chicken-04042b05.jpg
